{"type": "article", "id": 30351, "title": "护指小工具", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-31T22:57:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160731203021IjleJ09Y6chFMpbo.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>还在为徒手拆信、快递或是各种贝壳型包装头疼不已吗？来自英国的 <a href=\"http://version22.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Version 22</a> 工作室就设计了一款名为 Nimble 的护指小工具，戴上指尖后只需要简单的动作就能划开材料表面。它的原理在于那块小小的黑色陶瓷刀片，亮黄色的保护套则能够避免手指受到伤害。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/nimble-the-1-finger-wonder-tool-crafts#/\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 8 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731203046QYTD9ok1xqC8RBI5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707824\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731203046xQktaVfb0CAWyiHL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731203046tIfpyuHGoq2AgvhP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665037\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731203046kEfTwHA3Xc21LZvB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}